title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Afters with Josh Peskowitz
description:
On our new weekly lightning round mini ep with Josh Peskowitz, we’re fucking around with Jews, bosses, going out, stores, brands, funeral fits, stylish coworkers, Alexander Wang and much more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
